Give an example of a weighted graph on 6 vertices that \ldots








  has a unique minimum spanning tree.







\begin{tikzpicture}

\draw[thick] (-1,0) -- (1,0) -- (2,1) -- (3,0) -- (2,-1) -- (1,0);


